windy; Los Angeles 52 windy; Phoenix 51 fair; Salt Lake City 39
showers; San Diego 57 cloudy; San Francisco 44 windy; Seattle 35
rain.
   _Canada: Montreal 5 fair; Toronto 23 windy.
