<HEAD>Franco's Sister Dies</HEAD>
<DATELINE>MADRID, Spain (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   Pilar Franco, the sister of the late Spanish
ruler Gen. Francisco Franco, died Friday at the age of 94.
   She died from a cerebral hemorrhage after remaining in a coma for
