<HEAD>Woman Charged With Beating $11 Out Of Son To Buy Cocaine</HEAD>
<DATELINE>PHILADELPHIA (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   A woman accused of beating her 10-year-old
son with a metal pipe to get money for cocaine was arraigned Friday
on assault, theft and child endangerment charges, police said.
   Police said Joanne Oliphant, 29, beat her son, Jermaine, until he
